* bravado-core [does not honour](https://github.com/Yelp/bravado-core/blob/b192c199c7e7303a03ce0e07e11c5bfec25e9d2b/bravado_core/formatter.py#L92-L98) the [OpenAPI spec when it comes to bytes and binary formats](https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/blob/d3b582593a1f6092c8666ad7c893ae5e12779ec7/versions/2.0.md#data-types) - i.e. bytes is misinterpreted (it shall be base64) and binary is ignored;

