Hi All,
I just want to share what I have done before when facing problem in deploy using JHipster and some module need font-awesome.  During grunt process, configuration under index.html to load font-awesome.css are gone. so what I did is:
bower install --save font-awesome
(--save is to generate automatically configuration is used by font-awesome working fine)
go to bower.json and do some modification like below:
  "overrides": {
    "bootstrap": {
      "main": [
        "dist/js/bootstrap.js",
        "dist/css/bootstrap.css",
        "less/bootstrap.less"
      ]
    },
	"font-awesome": {
	  "main": [
		"css/font-awesome.css"
	  ]
	}
  }

After that run Grunt and working like what I want.

